# IMPORTANT — defense-in-depth policy
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# All scripts in this repo default their *runtime* output paths (reports,
# workspaces, logs, conversation state, examples/openhands-data, etc.) to
# locations OUTSIDE the working tree, under $HOME/openhands-deployment/.
# This file is the second line of defence: even if an operator overrides
# those defaults back inside the tree (e.g. WORKSPACE_BASE=./workspace),
# nothing here will be staged. Never weaken these rules.
# ============================================================================

# --- secrets / runtime config -----------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.local

# --- build / scan artifacts -------------------------------------------------
reports/
logs/
*.log
*.bak
*.bak.*
.scout-cache/

# --- workspaces / volumes (host-side runtime state) ------------------------
workspace/
data/
.openhands/

# --- legacy in-repo paths (pre-default-relocation; kept defensively) -------
examples/openhands-data/
examples/openhands.log
examples/.openhands/
examples/data/
examples/workspace/

# --- editor / OS noise ------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# --- node / python (in case a contributor adds tooling later) ---------------
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
